Paper: hep-th/9910141

Date: 1999-10-18

Title: Closed Path Integrals and Renormalisation in Quantum Mechanics

Authors: H. Jirari, H. Kr\"{o}ger, X.Q. Luo, K.J.M. Moriarty, and S.G. Rubin

Comments: Revised text, 1 figure added; Text (LaTeX file), 1 Figure (ps file)

Journal-ref: Phys.Rev.Lett. 86 (2001) 187-191

We suggest a closed form expression for the path integral of quantumtransition amplitudes. We introduce a quantum action with renormalizedparameters. We present numerical results for the $V \sim x^{4}$ potential. Therenormalized action is relevant for quantum chaos and quantum instantons.